longBusinessSummary: wallstreet:online AG operates wallstreet-online.de, a financial portal in Germany. The company's portal offers information on the topics of stock market, economy, and finance. It provides national and international market price data, charts, and insider data, as well as financial and analytical tools in the area of stock exchange and markets. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Berlin, Germany.
